---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const updated = 'May 15, 2026';
---
<Base
  title="Terms of Service | AIToolSpott"
  description="Terms of Service for AIToolSpott, including content usage, affiliate disclosures, third-party platforms, and acceptable use."
  slug="terms"
>
  <Header />

  <main class="flex-1">
    <section class="border-b border-brand-border/50 py-14">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <p class="text-brand-cyan text-sm font-semibold mb-3">AIToolSpott</p>
        <h1 class="font-display font-extrabold text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-white mb-4">
          Terms of Service
        </h1>
        <p class="text-brand-dim leading-relaxed">
          Last updated: {updated}
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p>
          These Terms of Service govern your access to and use of AIToolSpott, including
          our website, editorial content, newsletters, connected social channels, and any
          publishing or creator tools made available through the AIToolSpott brand.
        </p>

        <h2>Use of the Website</h2>
        <p>
          You may use AIToolSpott for lawful informational and editorial purposes only.
          You agree not to misuse the website, interfere with its normal operation, attempt
          unauthorized access, scrape the site in a harmful way, or use the site to violate
          any applicable law, platform rule, or third-party right.
        </p>

        <h2>Editorial Content</h2>
        <p>
          AIToolSpott publishes reviews, comparisons, ratings, tutorials, and opinionated
          editorial content about AI tools and software products. Our content is provided
          for general informational purposes and should not be treated as legal, financial,
          tax, investment, or professional advice.
        </p>

        <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
        <p>
          Some links on this website are affiliate links. If you click a qualifying link and
          purchase a product or service, AIToolSpott may earn a commission at no additional
          cost to you. These relationships do not guarantee placement, endorsement, or ranking.
        </p>

        <h2>No Warranty</h2>
        <p>
          The website and all content are provided on an &quot;as is&quot; and &quot;as available&quot; basis.
          We do not guarantee that the site will always be uninterrupted, accurate, secure,
          complete, or free from errors. Software vendors may change their products, pricing,
          features, and policies at any time.
        </p>

        <h2>Third-Party Services and Platforms</h2>
        <p>
          AIToolSpott may link to or integrate with third-party services such as YouTube,
          TikTok, Pinterest, analytics providers, email providers, hosting services, affiliate
          platforms, and advertising networks. Your use of those services is governed by their
          own terms, privacy policies, and platform rules.
        </p>

        <h2>User Submissions</h2>
        <p>
          If you contact us, subscribe to a newsletter, or otherwise submit information, you
          represent that the information you provide is accurate and that you have the right
          to provide it. You agree not to submit unlawful, abusive, infringing, or misleading
          material.
        </p>

        <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          Unless otherwise stated, the branding, layout, written content, original graphics,
          and editorial assets on AIToolSpott are owned by AIToolSpott or used with permission.
          You may not reproduce, republish, distribute, or commercially exploit substantial
          portions of the site without prior written permission.
        </p>

        <h2>Acceptable Use of Integrations</h2>
        <p>
          Any publishing workflows, creator tools, or connected platform integrations made
          available by AIToolSpott must be used in compliance with the applicable platform's
          developer policies, community guidelines, and content rules. Users must not use
          AIToolSpott integrations to post unlawful, deceptive, harmful, infringing, or
          prohibited content.
        </p>

        <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, AIToolSpott and its operators will not be
          liable for indirect, incidental, consequential, special, or punitive damages, or for
          any loss of profits, revenue, data, goodwill, or business opportunities arising from
          your use of the website or reliance on its content.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to the Service</h2>
        <p>
          We may modify, suspend, update, or discontinue any part of the website, related
          content, or connected integrations at any time without prior notice.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We may revise these Terms of Service from time to time. The latest version will be
          posted on this page with the updated effective date. Continued use of the site after
          changes become effective means you accept the revised terms.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For questions regarding these terms, contact AIToolSpott through the official website
          and public brand channels.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Base>
